<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/39210677-marilyn-basel"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1493826812i/39210677._UX100_CR0,24,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/39210677-marilyn-basel">Marilyn Basel</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">1996 edition San Diego, New York and London. My copy says USA on colophon page so my copy printed by Harcourt, Brace was printed in one of the first t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">1996 edition San Diego, New York and London. My copy says USA on colophon page so my copy printed by Harcourt, Brace was printed in one of the first two cities. Editions in Europe most likely say London.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
