<span id="freeTextContainer1077118884033196812">I know -- big deal, another poetry anthology. Still, I love this one because I dig the editor&apos;s tastes, and I love that he chose poetry that is life affirming. He says, &quot;I rejoice in being able to make an anthology as this one, and it may be a source of optimism that in this cruel century such an anthology could be made.&quot; Amen.</span>
