<span id="freeTextContainer13223912439312140900">So good. Every poem was new to me, and Milosz&apos; brief thoughts on each poem, it&apos;s magic, like having tea with him. A must read. Something I return to. A great consolation.</span>
  <span id="freeText13223912439312140900" style="display:none">So good. Every poem was new to me, and Milosz' brief thoughts on each poem, it's magic, like having tea with him. A must read. Something I return to. A great consolation.</span>
