<div id="review_697633646" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/697633646" />
    <a title="Martin lyon" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17148571-martin-lyon"><img alt="Martin lyon" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/697633646?book_show_action=true">Aug 17, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Martin lyon" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Martin lyon" href="/user/show/17148571-martin-lyon">Martin lyon</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer697633646" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15864113281239100779">The three poems I choose were: The August Afternoon<br/> The Window<br/> Black Meat<br/><br/><br/>I decided to choose The August Afternoon poem because my birthdays in August.<br/>I choose The Window because in books at night people always look at the window and freak.<br/>I choose Black Meat because I like eating meat for dinner.<br/>This book fits onto Three Poems or short stories from one anthology.<br/>I found all of them interesting. The August afternoon was about someone and his mother taking a walk. The Window is about a storm that </span>
  <span id="freeText15864113281239100779" style="display:none">The three poems I choose were: The August Afternoon<br /> The Window<br /> Black Meat<br /><br /><br />I decided to choose The August Afternoon poem because my birthdays in August.<br />I choose The Window because in books at night people always look at the window and freak.<br />I choose Black Meat because I like eating meat for dinner.<br />This book fits onto Three Poems or short stories from one anthology.<br />I found all of them interesting. The August afternoon was about someone and his mother taking a walk. The Window is about a storm that happened over night and cleared up in the morning. The Black Meat is about venison and the consumers. The character in The august afternoon I found interesting was the main character called I. The only character in the window was him. So him because of his virtuous thoughts. Black meat didn't have a character. My favourite quote from one of them was "The sum moved from behind the clouds, melting the hoarfrost". I like that quote because it means that the sun is so hot and bright that it melts the frost and vapour. I thought more deeply about what everyday has to offer and that you should make the most of it. So when you get a bad day you are still happy and fine. </span>
  <a data-text-id="15864113281239100779" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
